  The[0m[2m race condition[0m[2m is clear:[0m[2m multiple[0m[2m orders check[0m[2m stock simultaneously[0m[2m, all[0m[2m pass,[0m[2m all[0m[2m charge[0m[2m, but[0m[2m only some[0m[2m can[0m[2m decrement. Result[0m[2m: **7[0m[2m ghost[0m[2m charges** ($[0m[2m700 stolen[0m[2m from customers[0m[2m).
     
