     The fix[0m[2m works[0m[2m by[0m[2m:
     1[0m[2m. **[0m[2mAtomic[0m[2m reservation[0m[2m with[0m[2m lock[0m[2m**: `[0m[2mde[0m[2mcrement[0m[2m` now[0m[2m holds a[0m[2m lock,[0m[2m making[0m[2m it atomic[0m[2m
