     -[0m[2m **After**: decrement[0m[2m → charge[0m[2m → (rollback[0m[2m if[0m[2m needed[0m[2m) ([0m[2matomic reservation prevents[0m[2m overs[0m[2melling[0m[2m, rollback[0m[2m prevents[0m[2m ghost charges)[0m[2m
     
